trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of project output references belonging to a project item.
trans-unit.target: 表示属于某项目项的项目输出引用的集合。

trans-unit.source: If you attempt to add a project output reference that has the same deployment properties as an existing reference, then no new output reference is added.
trans-unit.target: 如果你尝试添加项目输出引用具有与现有的引用相同的部署属性，则不添加任何新的输出引用。

trans-unit.source: Instead, the existing reference is returned.
trans-unit.target: 相反，返回现有的引用。

trans-unit.source: The project to be added as a reference.
trans-unit.target: 要添加为引用的项目。

trans-unit.source: A type of deployment as specified by the DeploymentType enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: DeploymentType 枚举值指定的部署类型。

trans-unit.source: Adds an output reference to the project.
trans-unit.target: 将输出引用添加到项目中。

trans-unit.source: The reference is added as a build dependency to the current project and included as a part of the SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 引用作为生成依赖项添加到当前项目，并包含在 SharePoint 项目项内。

trans-unit.source: The reference that was added.
trans-unit.target: 已添加的引用。

trans-unit.source: Occurs if the <paramref name="project" /> parameter is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 当 <paramref name="project" /> 参数为 <see langword="null" /> 时发生。

trans-unit.source: Each project in a Visual Studio solution has a unique ID.
trans-unit.target: 在 Visual Studio 解决方案中，每个项目都具有唯一的 ID。

trans-unit.source: This parameter represents the ID of the project to be added as a reference.
trans-unit.target: 此参数表示要添加为引用的项目的 ID。

trans-unit.source: The project specified by <c>projectId</c> should be loaded in the solution for this method to work correctly.
trans-unit.target: 为了让此方法正常运行，解决方案中应加载 <c>projectId</c> 指定的项目。

trans-unit.source: A type of deployment as specified by the DeploymentType enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: DeploymentType 枚举值指定的部署类型。

trans-unit.source: Adds an output reference to the project specified by <paramref name="projectId" />.
trans-unit.target: 将输出引用添加到 <paramref name="projectId" /> 指定的项目。

trans-unit.source: The reference is added as a build dependency to the current project and included as a part of the SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 引用作为生成依赖项添加到当前项目，并包含在 SharePoint 项目项内。

trans-unit.source: The reference that was added.
trans-unit.target: 已添加的引用。

trans-unit.source: Occurs if no project with the specified <paramref name="projectId" /> is found.
trans-unit.target: 找不到任何具有指定 <paramref name="projectId" /> 的项目时会发生。

trans-unit.source: The project to be added as a reference.
trans-unit.target: 要添加为引用的项目。

trans-unit.source: The project should be loaded in the solution for this method to work correctly.
trans-unit.target: 为了让此方法正常运行，解决方案中应加载该项目。

trans-unit.source: A type of deployment as specified by the DeploymentType enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: DeploymentType 枚举值指定的部署类型。

trans-unit.source: Adds an output reference to the project.
trans-unit.target: 将输出引用添加到项目中。

trans-unit.source: The reference is added as a build dependency to the current project and included as a part of the SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 引用作为生成依赖项添加到当前项目，并包含在 SharePoint 项目项内。

trans-unit.source: The reference that was added.
trans-unit.target: 已添加的引用。

trans-unit.source: Occurs if the parameter <paramref name="projectFullPath" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 当参数 <paramref name="projectFullPath" /> 为 <see langword="null" /> 时会发生。

trans-unit.source: Occurs if the parameter <paramref name="projectFullPath" /> is <see langword="null" /> or no corresponding project could be found
trans-unit.target: 当参数 <paramref name="projectFullPath" /> 为 <see langword="null" /> 或找不到任何相应的项目时会发生

trans-unit.source: Clears the contents of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 清除集合的内容。

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the SharePoint project item.
trans-unit.target: 获取对 SharePoint 项目项的引用。

trans-unit.source: An object representing a SharePoint project item reference.
trans-unit.target: 表示 SharePoint 项目项引用的对象。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectOutputReference" /> reference to remove.
trans-unit.target: 要删除的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectOutputReference" /> 引用。

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified project output reference from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 从集合中删除指定的项目输出引用。

trans-unit.source: However, this method does not remove the project reference that was added by an <see langword="Add" /> method.
trans-unit.target: 但是，此方法不会删除 <see langword="Add" /> 方法添加的项目引用。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the remove operation succeeded; <see langword="false" /> otherwise.
trans-unit.target: 如果删除操作成功，则为 <see langword="True" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。
